@@TJvIconModifier.imOverlay
  The icon overlay of the file.
@@TJvIconModifier.imSelected
  The icon of the file when it's selected.
@@TJvIconModifier.imOpen
  The icon of the file when it's open.
@@TJvIconModifier.imShellSize
